ts/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲風係咁吹入嚟，個副機師就嚟跌出去，又耳鳴缺氧，又睇唔清儀器，咁都仲可以冷靜降落"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"仲要氣溫零下40度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89462600c21796ecbdaa34eec064e7ada407b27d","tid":665662,"uid":37566,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"劉傳健指出，擋風玻璃掉落後，首先面臨的就是失壓，突然的壓力變化會對耳膜造成很大傷害。溫度驟降到零下20-30度左右（監測顯示，當時飛機飛行高度為32000英尺，氣溫應該為零下40度左右），極度的寒冷會造成駕駛員身體凍傷。<br />\n<br />\n因此，他指出這次迫降是「非常難的一件事，不是一般的難。」只能依靠目視水平儀來進行操作；所幸駕駛艙失壓後，和客艙一樣會自動脫落氧氣面罩，缺氧問題不大。此外，駕駛艙和客艙是密封隔絕的，因此失壓、降溫沒有對乘客造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n屌你成篇潮文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215aa311883d629f7808e799cb22f7c7749f7721","tid":665662,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a49b82c9ac740d8c7c5a34c1c8cbc2c24a60056c","tid":665662,"uid":118463,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:05:24.000Z","msg":"個副駕真係嚇撚死<br />\n差d空中飛人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18fdb07e97ebf7fc03e2602d66ad9d86db51073","tid":665662,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:47:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"410525030b6a6d2761f300cc8e054d9085ea01e8","tid":665662,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1071b9b54cc4c1c032903b0bbe5b59d3ba24ae42","tid":665662,"uid":53139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da73a8bcf66746e2cbdd45a2c49c5b7ccf4c6385","tid":665662,"uid":53610,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTi